# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1191, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if you have platform-specific dependencies, it can be excluded.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Using Poetry requires nesting or sharing the lockfile, which is recommended.
